$MUDNAME$ Creator Help
query_connection

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
query_connection -  This method returns the connecting room for the given coordinates and direction.
.EP

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
string query_connection(string terrain,
int * co_ords,
string direc)
.EI

.SH Parameters
.SI 5
%^BOLD%^terrain%^RESET%^ - the terrain name
%^BOLD%^co_ords%^RESET%^ - the coordinates
%^BOLD%^direc%^RESET%^ - the direction to find the room for
.EI

.SH Returns
.SI 5
the file name of the connecting room or 0 if none was found
.EI

.SH Defined in
.SI 5
/handlers/terrain_handler.c
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5

This method returns the connecting room for the given coordinates and
direction.
.EP

